<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>It would be nice to be able to do (inside instanceof Zend_Form)</p>

<p>$dateValidate = Zend_Validate_Date(Zend_Date::DATE_FULL);</p>

<p>$this-&gt;addElement('text', 'date', array(
        'validators' =&gt; array($dateValidate)
    )
);</p>

<p>Now, you have to set the actual format.</p>

